0,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"立邦第二代超級五合一<br />\nColour code #0000<br />\n利伸油漆佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:50:09.000Z","msg":"一鑵油油到幾大幅牆?"},{"pid":"6518fd6527261145e5895f80afb9c6b708bda6f1","tid":1875190,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30f18d4890e3cbca9c3a826e9be4803b1a23ffe7","tid":1875190,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43e31de02e76b60671459e4367133bb94eebeec7","tid":1875190,"uid":6058,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"立邦第二代超級五合一<br />\nColour code #0000<br />\n利伸油漆佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:50:09.000Z","msg":"一鑵油油到幾大幅牆?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T18:58:12.000Z","msg":"其實睇係點油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係我<br />\n2或3升油大概都油到一間房仔唔包天花<br />\n至於卡裝油來計<br />\n我大概用兩卡油一間三百零四百尺屋嘅天花"},{"pid":"e0143d189b445436f67768b260fe57cae1a6f285","tid":1875190,"uid":70291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T20:11:14.000Z","msg":"有黑色可能係發毛，聽人講話要用漂白水抺一抺先殺左D菌，如果唔係會生番出黎(好似係)。<br />\n油漆搵人整最好一次過全屋整哂，上面巴打都講左其實價錢差唔遠，油完等乾既時間係最耐。<br />\n只係要諗下搬家私問題<br />\n如果間房甩得出黎，個廳應該都差唔多到期，所有甩得出黎既野全部都要整甩哂。無甩出就求其沙紙省下油番幾層面is ok。<br />\n同埋買油佔成本好少，唔好慳買隻好少少，買番原廠底漆(絲拿)好似會痴得實D。"},{"pid":"315d1d08b5b11e0c4a1aad8b9f1e5301007aec89","tid":1875190,"uid":70291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T20:11:40.000Z","msg":"between 點解會開係潮流台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833e9c0c9b87cd143620b6fff5d35b54437b80ce","tid":1875190,"uid":16362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"買可防潮"},{"pid":"f24e1f736da3fcce86a08b7cd650e35d493b1a6f","tid":1875190,"uid":135177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"761735ae4d3